    "updated_at": "2017-05-21T22:04:24Z",
    "body": "Is this still a problem in simple electron applications? You can try the RTL layout out with the `--force-ui-direction=rtl` command line argument. I ran into some problems with the default menu (locations calculated without respect to RTL, I have fixed that in the datalist PR), but the menu did not disappear for me when resizing."
